"space-opengl": partial port of my "space" prototype to C++ and OpenGL

Requires:
    freeglut3-dev (apt-get install freeglut3-dev)

Features:
    Ship, asteroids (no bullets or explosions).
    Smoothly interpolated animations.
    Multi-layer parallax starfield background.

Run "make" and "./main" to compile and run. Use the A and W keys to rotate the ship, use W key to accelerate forward.

